{"tid":2422700,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"遭警推跌孕妻之夫反被控 警稱中止行為不檢調查  馮生: 拘捕只屬「洩憤」","createTime":"2021-02-25T11:20:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T12:20:11.000Z","uid":56115,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"12dfb11a4ecf6a1f1ba3fc5c6b0d97c83c0aa819","tid":2422700,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T11:20:03.000Z","msg":"去年8.31襲擊事件一周年，旺角一帶有市民聚集，警方多次推進驅散，其間一度施放胡椒噴霧，並疑似「箍頸」拉跌當時懷孕7至8個月的馮太，令她倒地需召喚救護車到場送院，同行丈夫「中椒」更被涉嫌公眾地方行為不檢被捕。公民黨油尖旺區議會副主席余德寶今日（25日）在社交媒體表示，收到通知警方撤回對馮先生的調查，不會落案起訴。<span class=\"red\">馮生形容撤回控告再次證明警方濫捕，礙於警察投訴科功能有限，不會作投訴。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他指當日被警方以涉嫌公眾地方行為不檢拘捕，之後每個月都要到警署續保，令親友非常擔心，<span class=\"red\">「當然唔合理，拉我係想洩憤！因為我鬧佢哋！雖然我覺得唔大機會機會告得入，但煩到屋企人又要朋友擔心」。</span>"},{"pid":"9f57f77ce6bda8e7f297e66e5427b818ac853933","tid":2422700,"uid":56115,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T11:20:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210225/OFV5SHASIFBOJNFE222NE4RGZY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210225%2FOFV5SHASIFBOJNFE222NE4RGZY%2F&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFW6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=e1f3a14d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210225%2FOFV5SHASIFBOJNFE222NE4RGZY%2F&h=0bc49727\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210225/OFV5SHASIFBOJNFE222NE4RGZY/</a>"},{"pid":"8e6e0b219aab1d9dc986823253bca6687e0dbe12","tid":2422700,"uid":145273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T11:21:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"18e06a3fb549021a27cc79ddfe930622d8ea0158","tid":2422700,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T11:23:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17be4ec858641503693ace